You notice that the vehicle approaching you seems to be slowing down. You let out a sigh of relief.

When the vehicle gets closer, you begin to back up from the road. The vehicle stops and a man rolls down his window.

"Where you headed?" the man demanded.

This man gave you an immediate bad feeling, and you would honestly prefer a woman pick you up. However, should you really be this picky in this situation?

